snippet.title: Pair Up | Trailer [ENGLISH]
snippet.description:
Amazingly satisfying. Completely customizable. Pair Up is easy to play, difficult to master casual game that is a delight to all your senses. 

The perfect game on the go, Pair Up mashes the satisfaction of match two games with connecting puzzles to give you a satisfying casual experience you can bring everywhere. 

Feeling hungry? Looking for a cute animal to cuddle? Pair Up also features unlockable themes that let you customize your game to fit your moods. From cupcakes to burgers, kittens to rhinos - your favourite themes can be paired to your mood, location, or other fancies.
